d":160698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:04:50.000Z","msg":"錢黎架  <br />\n你叫飯民做d咁撚冇飯氣嘅嘢?<br />\n會做嘅唔叫飯民啦"},{"pid":"0fe255bc87436fe26481331ce5c3a2ef7ef61fc2","tid":497364,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5cb014d4e8a0eb0139819effbf25742cbe4aba1","tid":497364,"uid":143646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:06:30.000Z","msg":"而家總辭 到時又要選過咪一樣。。"},{"pid":"cc503237bb45da62c008245a804598eb0d77f766","tid":497364,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"原來你條撚屌就係鄭融大西洋，唔怪得d陰毒法似曾相識"},{"pid":"f29d1b38f9e24ff67444b01e6851f038f99c3d00","tid":497364,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>立法會無民意授權？then?<br />\n特首夠無民意授權 市民咪一樣對其有認受性</blockquote><br />\n要令到政府變為不義政府 無民意授權<br />\n就可以置諸死地而後生 <br />\n呢個講法只係空口說不話<br />\n事實上呢個世界好多政府都無民意授權 <br />\n但亦無半點管治上既動搖</blockquote><br />\ntrue<br />\n去到依一刻先總辭已經無意義<br />\n要做既話當初梁遊被dq就已經要做<br />\n依家基本上係死局，泛民一黎唔會捨得個位，二黎quit左都唔會有人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泛民依家仲係到咩今次唔會亂衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係議事規則一定會成功改到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實改埋議事規則，泛民係議內都已經名存實亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果佢地願意放棄十萬一個月，我覺得可以總辭。睇下社會上有咩聲音回響</blockquote><br />\n就當總辭嘅建議係無效<br />\n<br />\n咁而家客觀嚟講做又死唔做又死<br />\n唔做就一定死,而你嘅議席嘅價值只係在於你份糧嘅時候<br />\n咁點解唔試下做呢<br />\n定係你只係在意你份糧?</blockquote><br />\n你up乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咪已經答左自己個問題囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔做，因為<br />\n1.總辭嘅建議係無效<br />\n2.做又死唔做又死，做左都一定死</blockquote><br />\n其實議事規都改左既話<br />\n淨返既唯一用處應該係分組點票擋一擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一，都叫有些少用<br />\n第二，都係答唔到泛民總辭除左滿足佢想睇泛民仆街嘅欲望之外對件事會有咩幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6640bc452d9f4694c3e4c49856f7ddca3367b1","tid":497364,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"根本政棍毓民 = 五毛，想盡方幫手通過法案&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nBTW，佢既非和平應該係故意擲杯唔中先真喎，佢示範左架~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3a6517ba11cd06c72cebbc370a1c3d84ab2a0f","tid":497364,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本政棍毓民 = 五毛，想盡方幫手通過法案&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nBTW，佢既非和平應該係故意擲杯唔中先真喎，佢示範左架~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總唔總辭都過架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318f7c40ea46f7c9ac0d2c989cb3eea617d57cdd","tid":497364,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:27:56.000Z","msg":"毓民又教人焦土<br />\n<br />\n話佢唔係曲線幫共產黨都無人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有班傻仔信佢果套"},{"pid":"9e5ffe742353958a241fc39761b406e2666e7cb9","tid":497364,"uid":161243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"1. 總辭: 正!正苦唔洗再諗計一個一個去DQ;<br />\n2. 非和平:慈母以暴動罪名拉Q晒佢唔准保釋,然後一個一個去DQ;<br />\n<br />\n結果: 23-100條半晝一二三讀通過<br />\n<br />\n飯民:做緊垃圾會議員, 冇得做叫佢乞食(有正職除外)?<br />\n冇得做果D乞緊食都要批尖個柒頭想插番入去, 有D批到冇頭髮只傾唔砌都想插入去...<br />\n<br />\n死局一個"},{"pid":"07b114fd5e5e05ae59d26edc5998789a1f0a4c6f","tid":497364,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b721e8794c78cb3502028af84ed6f874ba04b61","tid":497364,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15bf1d4bf94301d54b8f8c2780b53db38c8f5aa0","tid":497364,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 總辭: 正!正苦唔洗再諗計一個一個去DQ;<br />\n2. 非和平:慈母以暴動罪名拉Q晒佢唔准保釋,然後一個一個去DQ;<br />\n<br />\n結果: 23-100條半晝一二三讀通過<br />\n<br />\n飯民:做緊垃圾會議員, 冇得做叫佢乞食(有正職除外)?<br />\n冇得做果D乞緊食都要批尖個柒頭想插番入去, 有D批到冇頭髮只傾唔砌都想插入去...<br />\n<br />\n死局一個</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得返暴力，不過又無夠多人，所以玩完"},{"pid":"351b16dbc31d8ae12bb83f1148d3cd031c97c150","tid":497364,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cd0beabc7d811336a211eea7cabc0d7e17fd12d","tid":497364,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"立中國國歌法。民主黨公民黨唔係諗點樣反對, 係幫政府諗點樣執法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/459958/4?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/459958/4?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主黨泛民係咪放棄咗爭取真普選?係咪知道香港一日未獨立都唔會有?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/490907/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/490907/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"bfe13b0e45d4231f8e370d920fbcbc93af197ad2","tid":497364,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"唔好話總辭，淨係唔開會（包括所有委員會，呈請書會）白袋人工泛民都唔會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13aebe3783892f8b582b4108873cf404fa1ac43c","tid":497364,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}